title: Stop Waiting.. || EP:107
description:
Hey Rehabbers, 
It's time for you to stop waiting. Stop waiting on the perfect time. Stop waiting on people. Stop waiting for opportunities to knock at your door. Truth is, Millions of people have DIED waiting. That can't be you. It's time for you to stop waiting and start creating. It's time for you to create the life that you want to live.
